snippet.title: Emil Chronicle Online Anime Trailer
snippet.description:
Heres a pretty cool anime trailer of the MMORPG 'Emil Chronicle Online' which came out a couple of years ago.

Its really BIG in Japan so BIG in fact it has its own card game, enjoy :P
